  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed roof extension by reason of its detailed design, siting, massing, bulk and height would form a dominant and discordant addition to the host locally listed building and wider terrace setting. The development would interrupt a predominantly unaltered rear roof line within this section of the terrace to a harmful degree and would be readily visible from the surrounding private realm causing harm to the character and appearance of the Arlington Square Conservation Area.  The proposed development s therefore considered to be contrary to policy CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy 2011, policies DM2.1 and DM2.3 of the Islington Development Management Policies 2013, guidance contained within Islington's Urban Design Guide 2017 & The NPPF 2019."
